"679","management and the Board of Trustees of Putnam Multi Cap"
"680","Growth Fund (formerly known as Putnam New Opportunities
Fund) and the Securities and Exchange Commission and is not"
"681","intended to be and should not be used by anyone other than"
"682","these specified parties."
