"697","Regulatory matters and litigation Putnam Mulit-Cap Growth Fund"
"698","6/30/11 Annual report"
"699","In late 2003 and 2004, Putnam Management settled charges brought"
"700","by the SEC and the Massachusetts Securities"
"701","Division in connection with excessive short-term trading in"
"702","Putnam funds. Distribution of payments from Putnam"
"703","Management to certain open-end Putnam funds and their"
"704","shareholders is expected to be completed in the next"
"705","several months. These allegations and related matters have"
"706","served as the general basis for certain lawsuits,"
"707","including purported class action lawsuits against Putnam"
"708","Management and, in a limited number of cases, some"
"709","Putnam funds. In May 2011, the fund received a payment of"
"710","$157,666 related to settlement of those lawsuits. Putnam"
"711","Management has agreed to bear any costs incurred"
"712","by the Putnam funds as a result of these matters."
